 result‚Üźobject(realevent SetEvent myevent)arg;after;before;event;pseudo;t;bat;aat;sys;custom
‚ćĚ Set up event-handling in a standard way

‚ćĚ Left and right arguments are provided directly from the ‚ąáonXxxx setting function
‚ćĚ All event names must be provided with case-sensitive canonical names (without "on" prefix)
‚ćĚ Left operand is a single Dyalog event name to be intercepted
‚ćĚ   If '', then only set the event handler text and don't intercept anything from Dyalog
‚ćĚ   If 'Event', then we're trying to intercept Dyalog-native events with their syntax ‚ćĚ? Feature to be added in the future
‚ćĚ Right operand is an APL+Win event name, optionally nested and followed by ordering criteria
‚ćĚ   Event names prefixed by ':' are "system events" rather than "user events"
‚ćĚ   Ordering criteria should be one or more other APL+Win event names prefixed by either "<" or ">".
‚ćĚ   The new event should be processed *after* any events named with a ">" prefix and *before* any events named with a "<" prefix.
‚ćĚ Example: result‚Üźobject ('Select' ##.##.SetEvent 'Click' '>MouseDown' '>MouseUp') arg

 :Section ‚ćĚ Validate non-user arguments (use ‚éēSIGNAL for SetEvent usage errors)
     myevent‚Üź,‚äÜmyevent ‚čĄ before‚Üź1‚Üď¬®myevent/‚ć®'<'=‚äÉ¬®myevent ‚čĄ after‚Üź1‚Üď¬®myevent/‚ć®'>'=‚äÉ¬®myevent ‚čĄ myevent/‚ć®‚Üź~myevent‚äÉ¬®‚ćõ‚ąä'<>' ‚ćĚ Decompose event list
     'No emulated event name provided'‚éēSIGNAL 5/‚ć®0=‚ČĘmyevent
     'Too many emulated event names provided'‚éēSIGNAL 5/‚ć®1<‚ČĘmyevent
     myevent‚Üź‚äÉmyevent ‚ćĚ We only set up one emulated event with a call here
     :if custom‚Üź(IsInt realevent)‚ąß0=‚Č°realevent ‚čĄ realevent‚Üź‚ćērealevent ‚čĄ :endif ‚ćĚ Allow for numeric custom event numbers
     'Improper specification of event names'‚éēSIGNAL 11/‚ć®0‚ąäIsChar¬®realevent myevent,before,after
     'Do not use "on" prefix on event names'‚éēSIGNAL 11/‚ć®(‚äā'on')‚ąä2‚ÜĎ¬®realevent myevent,before,after
     'Not an available native event name'‚éēSIGNAL 11/‚ć®(custom~‚ćõ‚ąß√ó‚ČĘrealevent)‚ąß~realevent‚äā‚ćõ‚ąä'Event',‚ć•‚äÜobject ‚ąÜWG'EventList'
     sys‚Üź':'‚ąämyevent ‚čĄ myevent~‚Üź':' ‚ćĚ Separate out the system-event signal
     result‚ÜźClasses.NoRes ‚ćĚ We'll pre-set result ahead of time in case of an early exit
 :EndSection

 :Section ‚ćĚ Return existing handler if requested
     :If sys~‚ćõ‚ąß0=‚ČĘarg
