         arg‚Üź‚ąÜdlt arg ‚ćĚ Ignore leading and trailing spaces
         object ‚éēVSET sys~‚ćõ/‚äā('_on',myevent)arg ‚ćĚ Set new APL+Win event handler text
         :If 0=‚ČĘrealevent
