 :EndSection

 :Section ‚ćĚ Obtain or initialize Dyalog-native event definition
     :If myevent‚Č°'Event' ‚ćĚ Are we setting up a pure Dyalog event?
         ‚ćĚ? This process hasn't been written yet, but works entirely differently than APL+Win events
     :Else
         event‚Üź0~‚ć®object ‚ąÜWG'Event'
         :If (‚ČĘevent)‚Č•t‚Üźrealevent‚ć≥‚ć®‚ć•‚äÜ{‚ćĶ‚Üď‚ć®2√ó'on'‚Č°2‚ÜĎ‚ćĶ}¬®‚äÉ¬®event
